## Design Notes ({{ design_style }})

{% if design_style == "minimal-clean" %}
- Form fields: clean `border border-gray-300 rounded-md` inputs, focus ring in accent color
- Labels: `text-sm font-medium text-gray-700`, no uppercase
- Error messages: `text-xs text-red-600`, inline below the field
- Submit button: solid accent color, label text only (no icon)
- Max form width: `max-w-2xl` centered, card-in-card layout avoided
{% elif design_style == "corporate-professional" %}
- Form fields: slightly inset look with gray background, defined borders
- Labels: `text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500`, prominent
- Required indicator: asterisk with tooltip explanation
- Error messages: red background strip across the top of the form (summary) + inline field errors
- Submit button: prominent, full-width at mobile, right-aligned at desktop
{% elif design_style == "playful-modern" %}
- Form fields: rounded-xl, soft shadow on focus, accent color border on active
- Labels: emoji prefix per field type, friendly copy ("What should we call you?")
- Error messages: shaking animation on submit with inline tooltip errors
- Submit button: gradient, rounded-xl, hover scale animation
- Success: confetti animation on create success
{% endif %}
